    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>18 November 1948</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 458</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">


<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-a519f345-fbb2-44e3-a401-cfdfc1b13516'>
            
<p class="">(by Private Notice)</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-d50e8575-80ab-40ed-b775-7cb9c7985b6e">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-d50e8575-80ab-40ed-b775-7cb9c7985b6e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-d50e8575-80ab-40ed-b775-7cb9c7985b6e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-d50e8575-80ab-40ed-b775-7cb9c7985b6e">
                
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d50e8575-80ab-40ed-b775-7cb9c7985b6e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-11-18/debates/23efb35b-f4a1-4e92-abee-079858e2ac03/EuropeanUnityCommittee(BritishRepresentatives)#contribution-d50e8575-80ab-40ed-b775-7cb9c7985b6e">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister whether he can inform the House of the names of the British representatives to sit on the Committee recently set up by the Governments of the live Brussels Treaty Powers to consider measures for the closer unity of Europe, and, in particular, the proposal to create a Consultative European Assembly without executive power.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d50e8575-80ab-40ed-b775-7cb9c7985b6e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-11-18/debates/23efb35b-f4a1-4e92-abee-079858e2ac03/EuropeanUnityCommittee(BritishRepresentatives)#contribution-d50e8575-80ab-40ed-b775-7cb9c7985b6e">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-270b7c19-f26f-4a27-811c-7364ef3666d2">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-270b7c19-f26f-4a27-811c-7364ef3666d2">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-270b7c19-f26f-4a27-811c-7364ef3666d2">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-270b7c19-f26f-4a27-811c-7364ef3666d2">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Attlee)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-270b7c19-f26f-4a27-811c-7364ef3666d2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-11-18/debates/23efb35b-f4a1-4e92-abee-079858e2ac03/EuropeanUnityCommittee(BritishRepresentatives)#contribution-270b7c19-f26f-4a27-811c-7364ef3666d2">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Hon. Members will doubtless have seen the announcement of the names in the Press <span id="566" class="column-number" data-column-number="566"></span> today. They are: The Chancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster, Lord Inverchapel, Sir Edward Bridges, Professor Wade and Mr. T. H. Gill.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-270b7c19-f26f-4a27-811c-7364ef3666d2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-11-18/debates/23efb35b-f4a1-4e92-abee-079858e2ac03/EuropeanUnityCommittee(BritishRepresentatives)#contribution-270b7c19-f26f-4a27-811c-7364ef3666d2">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-6e8138aa-8f60-479f-a9ea-df1a6bd1ff6b">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-6e8138aa-8f60-479f-a9ea-df1a6bd1ff6b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-6e8138aa-8f60-479f-a9ea-df1a6bd1ff6b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-6e8138aa-8f60-479f-a9ea-df1a6bd1ff6b">
                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-6e8138aa-8f60-479f-a9ea-df1a6bd1ff6b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-11-18/debates/23efb35b-f4a1-4e92-abee-079858e2ac03/EuropeanUnityCommittee(BritishRepresentatives)#contribution-6e8138aa-8f60-479f-a9ea-df1a6bd1ff6b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Did the right hon. Gentleman, in coming to this decision, take into consideration the fact that the formation of this Committee arose out of The Hague Conference—[HON. MEMBERS: "No."]—yes, out of The Hague Conference, and that the Chancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster did his utmost to prevent or spoil that Conference and was everywhere regarded as a protagonist against the policy of a united Europe except upon a Socialist basis?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6e8138aa-8f60-479f-a9ea-df1a6bd1ff6b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-11-18/debates/23efb35b-f4a1-4e92-abee-079858e2ac03/EuropeanUnityCommittee(BritishRepresentatives)#contribution-6e8138aa-8f60-479f-a9ea-df1a6bd1ff6b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-1d714650-2fa6-4463-9226-b26256421079">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-1d714650-2fa6-4463-9226-b26256421079">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-1d714650-2fa6-4463-9226-b26256421079">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-1d714650-2fa6-4463-9226-b26256421079">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1d714650-2fa6-4463-9226-b26256421079" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-11-18/debates/23efb35b-f4a1-4e92-abee-079858e2ac03/EuropeanUnityCommittee(BritishRepresentatives)#contribution-1d714650-2fa6-4463-9226-b26256421079">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I think the right hon. Gentleman is incorrect in two respects. The question of closer unity in Western Europe has been considered, not only by The Hague Conference, but by the Governments concerned, and very practical steps have been taken by this Government in that direction. Secondly, my right hon. Friend the Chancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster had certain views with regard to The Hague Conference, but he was always strong in his support of the idea of Western European collaboration.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1d714650-2fa6-4463-9226-b26256421079" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-11-18/debates/23efb35b-f4a1-4e92-abee-079858e2ac03/EuropeanUnityCommittee(BritishRepresentatives)#contribution-1d714650-2fa6-4463-9226-b26256421079">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-26877029-e445-4cd7-8ac5-be91f4271787">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-26877029-e445-4cd7-8ac5-be91f4271787">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
