        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">the phrase "controversial politics" comes entirely from the right hon. Gentleman. It is one of the right hon. Gentleman's curious prejudices that, if there happens to be a Labour Government, that is partisan, but, if there is a Conservative Government or a Government headed by himself, it is not partisan.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
